    "core_content": {
      "parsing_res_list": [
        {
          "block_label": "header",
          "block_content": "第10天释迦便当皆美味浮潜露营印象深",
          "block_bbox": [
            390,
            57,
            745,
            78
          ],
          "block_id": 0,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "number",
          "block_content": "|143 |",
          "block_bbox": [
            784,
            62,
            818,
            82
          ],
          "block_id": 1,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "",
          "block_bbox": [
            89,
            146,
            830,
            691
          ],
          "block_id": 2,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "台东盛产一种叫“释迦”的水果，我在广州也见过，叫“番荔枝”。对它印象深刻，不是因为名字古怪，而是因为价格非一般的贵。这种水果，外皮突起恰似佛头，故有赖球果、佛头果、释迦果之称。",
          "block_bbox": [
            84,
            707,
            411,
            963
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": 1
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "沿途经过村镇时，不时见",
          "block_bbox": [
            134,
            978,
            409,
            1000
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "",
          "block_bbox": [
            421,
            705,
            821,
            994
          ],
          "block_id": 5,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "到路边有摆卖释迦的农舍。我在心中琢磨着，到这里了还不品尝一下，似乎太对不起自己。\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            88,
            1017,
            817,
            1077
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "看中一个大户人家，大大的凉棚，路边摆放着一筐筐的释迦，平板上也摆满了，个个硕大饱满，颇为招惹人啊！\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            88,
            1094,
            817,
            1153
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "一打听，价格果然不菲，新台币要100元一斤。",
          "block_bbox": [
            132,
            1170,
            605,
            1192
          ],
          "block_id": 8,
          "block_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "我让老板娘特意挑选了一粒成熟的释迦给我，75元成交。",
          "block_bbox": [
            131,
            1209,
            707,
            1230
          ],
          "block_id": 9,
          "block_order": 6
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "“这个怎么吃啊？！”我也不怕老板娘笑话我，没吃过就是没吃过，",
          "block_bbox": [
            122,
            1246,
            811,
            1266
          ],
          "block_id": 10,
          "block_order": 7
        }
      ],
      "markdown": "",
